NK125(co)004:1: // d+harma sh+r+ai rang nyid kyi chos dang rjes su 'brel
NK125(co)004:2: ba'i spyod pa las brtsams pa'i lo rgyus bden gtam
NK125(co)004:3: rna ba'i bdud rtsi zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK125(co)004:5: rang nyid kyi chos dang rjes su 'brel ba'i spyod
NK125(co)004:6: pa las brtsams pa'i lo rgyus bden gtam rna ba'i
NK125(co)004:8: skyabs kun 'dus pa'i ngo bo rje btsun bla ma
NK125(co)004:9: dam pa'i zhabs la phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs su mchi'o
NK125(co)004:10: // rab 'byams rgyal ba kun gyi ye shes dang //
NK125(co)004:11: tha dad ma dmigs gcig chog chos kyi rje //
NK125(co)004:12: gter chen bla ma 'gyur med rdo rje'i zhabs //
NK125(co)004:13: dad brgya'i gtsug gi pad+mosa rtag tu mchod //
NK125(co)004:14: gang thugs 'gyur med kun khyab rdo rje'i khams //
NK125(co)004:15: mtha' dag dngos kun rjes zhugs chos kyi sku'i //
NK125(co)004:16: rnam thar rang rig ngo bor dbyer med pa'i //
NK125(co)004:17: bde chen mnyam nyid rtogs pa'i bka' drin stsol //
NK125(co)004:18: tshur mthong bdag 'dra'i blun rmongs spyod tshul rnams //
NK125(co)004:19: kun gyi gtan la phebs mod bzang po'i gtam //
NK125(co)004:20: med la sgro btags brjod pa'ang dgos med phyir //
NK125(co)004:21: 'di brjod dus dang blo gros gron pa'i rgyu //
NK125(co)004:22: 'on kyang gdod ma'i gshis lugs rang rig dbyings //
NK125(co)004:23: rnam 'gyur du ma'i 'char sgo ma 'gags kyang //
NK125(co)004:24: de don rtogs pa'i blo ngor mkha' lam ngos //
NK125(co)004:25: chu 'dzin dengs bzhin gnyis 'dzin gzeb las sgrol //
NK125(co)004:26: de phyir rang gsal gtad med 'gyu ba'i sems //
NK125(co)004:27: blo chung re dogs go rar ma bcug par //
NK125(co)004:28: rang tshul bden gtam dam pa'i gsung gi ngor //
NK125(co)004:29: 'dzem med smra'o rna ba'i bdud rtsir longs //
NK125(co)004:30: de la 'dir rang gi rnam thar rang rgyus kyi
NK125(co)004:31: sgo nas cung zad gleng ba la rigs kyi nus
NK125(co)004:32: pa nyid dkar po'i las kyis sad tshul /
NK125(co)004:33: de ltar sad pa las lus rten 'di btsas nas na tshod 'phel tshul /
NK125(co)004:34: bstan pa la zhugs nas thos sam gyis rgyud sbyangs tshul /
NK125(co)004:35: ji ltar thos pa'i don nyams su blangs tshul /
NK125(co)004:36: rang nus dang sbyar ba'i gzhan don cha tsam bsgrub tshul /
NK125(co)004:37: lhag pa'i bsam pas don gnyis 'grub 'gyur la smon lam ji ltar btab tshul dang drug las /
NK125(co)004:38: dang po ni rang gi sems nyid gdod ma'i gshis
NK125(co)004:39: lugs rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa gser bzang
NK125(co)004:41: de'i steng du theg pa gsum gyi rigs nus yod pa las /
NK125(co)004:42: theg pa chen po'i rigs kyi nus pa de /
NK125(co)004:43: tshe rabs snga ma'i rnam dkar gyi las cung zad
NK125(co)004:44: sbyangs shing smon lam gyi sems pa cung zad yod
NK125(co)004:45: pas sad de skye srid 'dir ye shes kyi sku
NK125(co)004:46: can rje btsun bla ma bka' drin mtshungs med gter
NK125(co)004:47: chen chos kyi rgyal po dang /
NK125(co)004:48: sdom btsun mkhas pa chen po rgyal ba'i sras po ste /
NK125(co)004:49: bla ma dam pa sku mched kyi gcung du skyes
NK125(co)004:50: pas chung ngu nas dam pa'i chos dang mjal ba'i
NK125(co)004:51: skal ba thob / de yang rje bla ma'i gter lung las /
NK125(co)004:52: g.yu sgra'i sprul pa blo ldan d+harma'i mingah zhes dang /
NK125(co)004:53: rgyal mo g.yu sgra'i sprul pa nih me khams sh+r+ai
NK125(co)004:54: las kyi ming zhes 'byung ba ltar d+harma sh+r+ai'i ming
NK125(co)004:55: dang / smyos kyi rus khams ji me yin par ma zad /
NK125(co)004:56: lo snying rta'i srog khams kyang me yin pas sbyar rung ba ltar /
NK125(co)004:57: gter 'byung lo rgyus su rje bla ma nyid kyis
NK125(co)004:58: ngos 'dzin par mdzad pa'i skal bzang thob pa ni
NK125(co)004:59: / sprul pa dngos yin par dka' yang /
NK125(co)004:60: rgyud byin gyis brlabs pa tsam la dgongs par mngon zhing /
NK125(co)004:61: de ltar brlabs pa'i yul yang dkar po'i rigs sad pa zhig dgos pa las /
NK125(co)004:62: de'i rtags snga ma'i bag chags bzang bar mtshon pa ni /
NK125(co)004:63: rang lo gnyis gsum tsam gyi tshe lus gnad lta
NK125(co)004:64: stangs byed pa sogs bsam gtan gyi bag chags 'dra
NK125(co)004:65: ba yod zer kyang rang gis ma dran /
NK125(co)004:66: byis pa'i dus dran pa rnyed pa tsam nas bzung
NK125(co)004:67: spyir skyes bu dam pa'i rigs dang bye brag karma
NK125(co)004:68: pa yab sras la bcos min gyi dad pa rang
NK125(co)004:70: phyis rtsa rgyud gsang snying la thos bsam byed dus
NK125(co)004:71: rog pa'i yig cha 'dra mthong ba las go ba'i
NK125(co)004:72: rne rnyed pa zhig byung ba la dpag na /
NK125(co)004:73: de dag gi slob rigs chos la bag chags cung zad bzhag pa zhig e yin snyam /
NK125(co)004:74: gang ltar yang chos rigs su skyes par brten byis
NK125(co)004:75: pa'i dus nas kyang dad pa dang snying rje dang
NK125(co)004:76: nges 'byung sogs che rab yod cing /
NK125(co)004:77: 'jig rten gyi bya ba la blo mi 'jug pas
NK125(co)004:78: tshe 'di bltas kyi dngos zhen rang bzhin gyis srab
NK125(co)004:79: pa 'di ni dkar po'i las kyis rigs sad pa'i
NK125(co)004:80: rtags su mtshon nus pa yin no //
NK125(co)004:81: gnyis pa lus rten 'di btsas nas na tshod 'phel tshul ni /
NK125(co)004:82: kho bo cag gi rus ni sngags rus te /
NK125(co)004:83: mthing ma smyos zhig chen po'i rigs rgyud yin /
NK125(co)004:84: lus 'di bskyed pa'i pha ma ni /
NK125(co)004:85: gnubs chen gyi yang srid yab rje smyos ston gsang bdag chen po phrin las lhun grub dang /
NK125(co)004:86: shes dkar rdo rje mtsho'i sprul pa ma btsun rje rigs lha 'dzin dbyangs can sgrol ma ste /
NK125(co)004:87: yab yum de gnyis las rje bla ma dam pa sku mched kyi gtsos pa'i sras lnga dang /
NK125(co)004:88: sras mo gnyis te sras lcam sring bdun 'khrungs pa las bdag lnga pa yin /
NK125(co)004:89: de yang shing pho rta'i lo la yul g.yor po
NK125(co)004:90: grwa nang gi lung pa'i sa tshigs sngags kyi sde
NK125(co)004:91: dgon dar rgyas chos gling zhes bya bar skyes /
NK125(co)004:92: ming rgyu skar gyi rten 'brel las legs pa don 'grub tu btags /
NK125(co)004:93: lo ngo gsum tsam la sleb dus bu rdzi'i gdol
NK125(co)004:94: spyod kyis grib phob ste lce mi bde ba 'di
NK125(co)004:95: byung / lcags pho byi bar phal cher rang gi gzhis dgon pa dang /
NK125(co)004:96: res zhang po'i khyim zlum po gnyis su bsdad /
NK125(co)004:97: skabs shig ma rin po che'i a ne'i rtsar khrab mor kyang phyin /
NK125(co)004:98: lo brgyad pa la gcen rgyal ba'i sras po'i zhabs
NK125(co)004:99: phyir dkris te dgun dpyid gnyis 'phyong rgyal dpal ri
NK125(co)004:100: dang / dbyar dbus ri'i gnas chen mchims phur bsdad /
NK125(co)004:101: de dus ma rin po che bsam yas su phebs
NK125(co)004:102: pa dang lhan cig bsam yas ri mthil gyi gnas
NK125(co)004:103: rten ngo mtshar ba rnams mjal zhing smon lam btab
NK125(co)004:104: / ma phyir theg rjes gcen dang dge slong legs
NK125(co)004:105: pa gnyis kyi rtsar klog sbyang la sbyang lo byas
NK125(co)004:106: / / gzhis nas keg sel gyi rim gror ming bsgyur dgos pa'i bka' phrin byung bar lta /
NK125(co)004:107: sprul sku phrin las rnam rgyal gcen gyi zhabs bsnyung bskor du phebs dus /
NK125(co)004:110: ming sprul sku rin po che la zhus pas 'thad
NK125(co)004:111: ces bskul ba ltar ming zhus pas pad+ma phrin las
NK125(co)004:113: gcen 'phyong rgyas su phyir phebs kyi zhabs phyir bsam yas mthil gyi bar 'ong nas /
NK125(co)004:114: rta mgrin gling du gsung sprul rin po che yab sras mjal /
NK125(co)004:115: de nas nged kyis zur mkhar gyi ko bar thon /
NK125(co)004:116: rta bsu ma sleb pas grwa phyi tshogs 'dus su zhag gnyis bsdad de gzhis su 'byor /
NK125(co)004:117: de dus rje bla ma dam pa'ang gtsang rong bon lung nas phyir phebs grub 'dug /
NK125(co)004:118: a ma yab sras lhan cig tu bzhugs pa mjal zhing /
NK125(co)004:119: gsung sbrul rin po che phyir lam grwa rgyud khrab mo zhol khrod du bzhugs 'dug pa'i sar /
NK125(co)004:121: ming o rgyan grags pa bzang po zhes stsal /
NK125(co)004:122: chab ze gshegs sar phyin nas dad pa chen pos tsan ner gsang chab zhus te mang du 'thung /
NK125(co)004:123: rang lo dgur sleb pa chu stag dbo zla'i nyer
NK125(co)004:124: gnyis la yab rje gsang bdag chen po ye shes
NK125(co)004:125: go 'pho'i rtags ngo mtshar ba dang bcas te dag
NK125(co)004:126: pa'i zhing du gshegs pa'i gdung mchod kyi tshe sku
NK125(co)004:127: gdung rin po che'i drung du yang yang phyin te
NK125(co)004:128: / phyag mang po btsal zhing gsol ba btab pas byin rlabs zhugs pa yin 'dra /
NK125(co)004:129: nub gcig yab rje bar snang la yer gyi gshegs
NK125(co)004:130: pa'i sku'i 'thu ba la 'jus pas rang yang bar
NK125(co)004:131: snang la had kyis btegs pa dang lhan cig gnyid
NK125(co)004:133: de ltar yab rje rig 'dzin chen po dang 'grogs
NK125(co)004:134: yun lo dgu'i ngo mthong tsam las ma byung bas
NK125(co)004:136: gcen rig 'dzin gter ston chen pos 'jig rten phyogs nas pha'i dod dang /
NK125(co)004:137: chos phyogs nas bka' drin gsum ldan gyi bla ma
NK125(co)004:138: mdzad nas brtse ba chen po'i spyan ras kyis btsa'
NK125(co)004:139: bas rjes su bzung ste legs par bskyangs /
NK125(co)004:140: gcen rgyal ba'i sras po dang /
NK125(co)004:141: ma rin po che nas kyang chung dus nas blo
NK125(co)004:142: ngan lam du ma btang bar chos sgor 'dren pa'i
NK125(co)004:144: mgrin pa theg pa nas chos la mos pa thob cing /
NK125(co)004:145: bsam pa rnyed pa nas bzung ste dam pa'i chos
NK125(co)004:146: la ngang gis 'jug tu yod pa'i skal ba thob
NK125(co)004:148: gsum pa bstan pa la zhugs nas thos bsam gyis rgyud sbyangs tshul ni /
NK125(co)004:149: rang lo bcu gsum pa la lus bsgyur zhing rje gter chen bla ma la gtsug phud phul te /
NK125(co)004:150: ming bstan 'dzin 'jam dbyangs dbang po zhes stsal /
NK125(co)004:151: skyabs gsum 'dzin pa'i dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa'ang thob /
NK125(co)004:152: bco lnga pa la gcen rgyal ba'i sras po rin
NK125(co)004:153: po che dang mnyam du rkang 'gros kyi chu bor
NK125(co)004:154: brgyud pho brang chen por phyin /
NK125(co)004:155: de dus rje bla ma nyid gong sa thams cad
NK125(co)004:156: mkhyen pa lnga pa chen pos ti sh+r+ai bzhes nas
NK125(co)004:157: chos bka' 'bul ba'i skabs na 'dug pa zhabs phyir
NK125(co)004:158: bsdad cing / rje thams cad mkhyen pa lnga pa chen po las rab tu byung ste /
NK125(co)004:159: ming ngag dbang chos dpal zhes stsal zhing dge tshul gyi sdom pa dang /
NK125(co)004:160: rang lo nyi shu pa chu glang lor slar yang pho brang chen por phyin te bsnyen rdzogs zhus /
NK125(co)004:161: phyis gong sa'i lung gis snga 'gyur gyi bstan pa'i
NK125(co)004:162: 'brel dang bcas smad 'dul ba'i sdom rgyun rnam par
NK125(co)004:163: dag pa kha rag zhal snga nas la bzhugs shing
NK125(co)004:164: khong 'dul ba'i ngang tshugs kyang bzang bas der bskyar
NK125(co)004:165: bsgrub gyis zhes bskul ba ltar rang lo nyer bdun
NK125(co)004:166: pa lcags sprel lo nag zla'i tshes bcu gsum gyi
NK125(co)004:167: nyi ma brgyad cha lus pa grib tshod skyes bu
NK125(co)004:168: gcig dang rkang pa gnyis kyi dus su rje bla
NK125(co)004:169: ma thams cad mkhyen pa'i mtshan dpe'i snang bas khyab
NK125(co)004:170: pa'i gnas dbu ru gru 'dzin gyi pho brang chen
NK125(co)004:171: por don gyi slad du mtshan nas smon na mkhan
NK125(co)004:172: chen dkon mchog bstan 'dzin las dad pa'i dge 'dun
NK125(co)004:173: grangs tshang ba'i dbus su tshigs gsum bar ma chad
NK125(co)004:174: pa'i cho ga'i bsnyen par rdzogs pa dge slong gi
NK125(co)004:175: dngos por bsgrubs / me yos nag zla'i nang du
NK125(co)004:176: rje gter chen bla ma las byang sdom bka' srol
NK125(co)004:177: gsum gyi smon 'jug sems bskyed dang /
NK125(co)004:178: rang lo bcu gnyis pa shing sbrul zla ba bdun
NK125(co)004:179: pa'i nyer lnga la rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor du
NK125(co)004:180: rig 'dzin thugs thig gi dbang nod pas rgyud smin
NK125(co)004:181: par byas te / rjes su thob pa'i so byang
NK125(co)004:182: gi sdom pa gnyis po de yang sngags sdom las
NK125(co)004:183: phye ba'i dang de'i sdom pa'i ngo bor skyes pas
NK125(co)004:184: sdom pa gsum gyi rang rgyud bsdam pa yin la
NK125(co)004:185: par byas te / / de yang rang nyid ma'i
NK125(co)004:186: pang du 'tsho ba'i dus nas yab rjes bka' dgongs
NK125(co)004:187: pad gling gi dbang phal mo che sogs dbang bka'
NK125(co)004:188: mang du thob par mdzad 'dug kyang bla ma dam
NK125(co)004:189: pa'i sngags rgya ting nge 'dzin gyi nus pas byin
NK125(co)004:190: gyi brlabs pa'i rten 'brel rang rgyud la sgrigs na'ang
NK125(co)004:191: par byas te / / / rang na gzhon zhing
NK125(co)004:192: 'dun pa zhan pas dbang gi brda don 'phrod dka'
NK125(co)004:193: bas na lus rten 'di la brda don phrod pa'i
NK125(co)004:194: dbang gis rgyud smin par byas pa ni thugs thig
NK125(co)004:195: gi dbang 'di nyid yin pas 'di ltar smos pa
NK125(co)004:196: par byas te / / / ste / de dus
NK125(co)004:197: bum nang du me tog lhung ba myu gu sdong
NK125(co)004:198: po snye ma'i bar du smin pa dang me tog
NK125(co)004:199: gi char 'bebs shing snyan pa'i sgra ldir ba sogs
NK125(co)004:200: ngo mtshar ba'i rtags kyang mngon du snang bar mdzad
NK125(co)004:202: nub rang gi rmi lam du'ang gos dkar gyon te
NK125(co)004:203: bu mo rgyan can mang po dang 'grogs nas ri
NK125(co)004:204: bo chen po'i ngos la 'dzegs shing nyi ma'i dkyil
NK125(co)004:206: de ltar bstan pa'i sgor zhugs te /
NK125(co)004:207: sdom pa gsum gyis rgyud legs par bsdams nas /
NK125(co)004:208: de rnams kyi snga phyi ci rigs par thos bsam gyis rgyud sbyangs tshul ni /
NK125(co)004:209: yab rje sku gshegs rting lo gsum tsam gyi bar
NK125(co)004:210: gcen bla ma dam pa sku mched dang ma rin
NK125(co)004:211: po che rnams phal cher phyogs theg 'ba' zhig gis
NK125(co)004:212: gzhis su bzhugs ma khoms pas /
NK125(co)004:213: de bar ma yi zhal ta ma bsam 'grub chos 'dzom gyis bskul te /
NK125(co)004:214: ngag bslab kyis gsol 'debs le'u bdun ma sogs dgon ba'i 'don chos kyi skor dang /
NK125(co)004:215: gsol dpon mchog gyur las yi ge 'bri klog /
NK125(co)004:216: dbu mdzad bstan 'dzin thos bsam gyis nam khoms dpe
NK125(co)004:217: rgyugs sdeb len gyis rang lugs kyi chog khrigs rnams
NK125(co)004:219: dgon pa'i dgun gyi mtsham sgrigs gcig gi thog /
NK125(co)004:220: rang gi blta dper pad gling bla ma'i las byang ma bu dang /
NK125(co)004:221: mkhas mchog gi dper mgon po sde brgyad kyi bskang gso chen mo sogs dpe cha kha shas dang /
NK125(co)004:222: gsol dpon mchog gyur gyi dbang phyug nyer brgyad kyi tsakli rnams bris /
NK125(co)004:223: de yang chung dus nas shes rig mi bkra zhing
NK125(co)004:224: ngag mi bde ba 'di yod pas yon tan mkhan
NK125(co)004:225: yong ba'i re chen po zhig med kyang sngon gyi
NK125(co)004:226: las 'phros mtshams sbyar nas stes 'grigs pa lta bus
NK125(co)004:227: / rang lo bcu gnyis pa la mes nor bu dar rgyas kyis mtshams sbyar te /
NK125(co)004:228: mnga' ris gung thang gi mkhas pa chen po bshes gnyen rnam rgyal dgon par phebs nas /
NK125(co)004:229: gcen bla ma dam pa sku mched kyis sgra rig
NK125(co)004:230: snyan ngag sogs gzhung lugs mang po gsan par mdzad
NK125(co)004:231: pa'i dus su bdag gis kyang ka l+aa pa'i mtshams
NK125(co)004:232: sbyor lnga'i ri mo tsam dang /
NK125(co)004:233: bod yig bskyar slob byas pa gcen rgyal sras rin
NK125(co)004:234: po ches phral phral gyi zhal ta dang phyag 'beb
NK125(co)004:235: sogs bskul lcag gnang bas yi ge tshug ma dang
NK125(co)004:236: gshar bris gnyis ka byang bar shes /
NK125(co)004:237: de'i phyi lo gung thang pan chen slar yang phebs
NK125(co)004:238: pa ka l+aa pa'i bshad pa dang sa ris zhus
NK125(co)004:239: nas / yongs rdzogs kyi ri mo'i rgyug blo thog
NK125(co)004:240: nas gtsang dag sdeb 'bul byas pa tshar ba'i nyin
NK125(co)004:241: nas / / de ring nyi shu drug yin pas
NK125(co)004:242: sa pan bltams pa'i dus chen dang ma sgrigs 'grigs
NK125(co)004:244: da dus kyi sgra pa ming che che mo 'di
NK125(co)004:245: ba tsho'i sgra yongs rdzogs las 'u cag gi mtshams
NK125(co)004:246: sbyor kyang dga' bar yod pas da mjug bskyangs te
NK125(co)004:247: ma brjed par mdzod cig gsungs dgyes dgyes mdzad /
NK125(co)004:248: de rjes sdebs sbyor gyi bshad pa dang /
NK125(co)004:249: zhwa lu lo chen gyi ka l+aa pa'i spyi t+aika gnyis kyi lung /
NK125(co)004:250: lany+tsa dang wa rtu la'i yi ge sogs yig sna 'ga' re'i phyag khrid /
NK125(co)004:251: rting sor bzang yul grong gsar du sum rtags kyi
NK125(co)004:252: bshad pa'ang zhus te brda sprod yan lag dang bcas
NK125(co)004:254: bcu dgu pa la zlum por mes rtsis rigs pa
NK125(co)004:255: chen po don 'grub dbang rgyal gyi drung du zla
NK125(co)004:257: dgu matha'i bsgyur 'god nas brtsams zhal lung ma bu
NK125(co)004:258: tshang ba'i dkar rtsis rnams nyin dang por sa ris
NK125(co)004:259: / mtshan la dri ba'i phra gcod dang /
NK125(co)004:260: zhun mar la brten nas dpe 'bri ba sogs snang mun 'khor yug tu 'bad par byas /
NK125(co)004:261: slob dpon spyan 'grib pas thog mar sa ris kyi bsgyur 'god rnams dka' tshegs che bar byung na'ang /
NK125(co)004:263: rang gi 'dun brtson drag po lta bus dkar rtsis la blo legs par 'byongs /
NK125(co)004:264: de zhor dbyangs 'char gyi bshad pa rags tsam dang
NK125(co)004:265: 'khor lo'i ngo sprod 'byung rtsis kyi rde'u dgram pa
NK125(co)004:266: rnams bslabs shing / gcen rgyal sras rin po che las kyang rtsis kyi go ba'i phra gcod dag /
NK125(co)004:267: rgya ston karma kun mkhyen la dus 'khor 'jig rten
NK125(co)004:268: bstan le las rag tsam dang rtsis kyang bsdus pa'i
NK125(co)004:269: bshad pa / sdeb sbyor gyi ngo mtshar ba'i sbyor ba rnams zhus /
NK125(co)004:270: phyis grwa phyir stag lung pa grub chen ngag dbang
NK125(co)004:271: gzungs chog la dbyangs can b+y+aa ka ra na'i sa
NK125(co)004:272: ris / tsan+d+ra pa'i yi ge'i bsdu ba dang /
NK125(co)004:273: ting mtha' sogs la zhi ba bshad dang /
NK125(co)004:274: gzhung spyi la yang bshad pa yam tsam zhig /
NK125(co)004:275: sde ba sbyor gyi yang ba'i bya ba rnams nyan /
NK125(co)004:276: rje gter chen bla ma'i drung du snyan ngag me long gi bshad pa zhus shing /
NK125(co)004:277: le'u gsum ka'i rtsom rgyugs kyang phul //
NK125(co)004:278: de la spyir rang lo bcu bzhi yan nas dar gling du ban gtsang ba brgyad grwa zhig dang /
NK125(co)004:279: de steng bcu bdun pa'i thog 'og min o rgyan
NK125(co)004:280: smin grol gling pa'i grwa gtsang gsar du tshugs skabs
NK125(co)004:281: grwa khyur zhugs te grwa pa'i 'don chos skor gyi
NK125(co)004:282: dpe 'dzin dang / gar thig dbyangs gsum gyi phyag bzhes rnams byang bar sbyangs shing /
NK125(co)004:283: de dag gi dus skabs ci rigs par spos khang
NK125(co)004:284: pa rin chen rgyal mtshan gyis mdzad pa'i sher phyin
NK125(co)004:285: gyi 'grel rkang dang don bdun cu'i bshad pa /
NK125(co)004:286: sa pan gyi sdom gsum rab dbye /
NK125(co)004:287: bla ma rgyal ba'i dge slong gi bslab bya rnams blo la zin cing /
NK125(co)004:288: gcen rgyal ba'i sras po las 'dul ba'i lag len
NK125(co)004:289: dang brda chad rnams bsgrim pa'i blos mnyan nas chub
NK125(co)004:290: par byas / rang lo nyi shu ba la grwa tshang gi dge bskos las sne dang /
NK125(co)004:291: nyer gcig pa shing stag gi lor rgyal sras rin po che sku gshegs pas /
NK125(co)004:292: de phyin nas grwa tshang gi rgyun tshogs dang sku rim sogs kyi slob dpon byed dgos byung bas /
NK125(co)004:293: snga dgong dang nub mo'i chos grwa 'grim pa dang /
NK125(co)004:294: tshogs 'du sogs dge 'dun rnams dang lhan cig dbang
NK125(co)004:295: po 'dul ba'i spyod lam bstum pa tsam las bslab
NK125(co)004:296: gnyer rus 'thon pa ma byung bar yun ring 'das
NK125(co)004:297: / rang lo nyer bdun pa'i thog rje bla ma sha 'ug gi gter sgrub la bzhugs pa las /
NK125(co)004:298: nang mtshams grol ba'i bag seng gi khog tu grwa
NK125(co)004:299: tshang gi rgan 'go rnams bos nas zhal ta phebs
NK125(co)004:300: par / 'don chos dang sngags kyi lag len byang
NK125(co)004:301: 'grongs pa tsam gyis chog shes par byas nas gar
NK125(co)004:302: yang mi phyin pas mdo sngags kyi gzhung lugs rnams
NK125(co)004:303: rang blo'i theg tshad dang sbyar ba'i thos bsam re
NK125(co)004:304: dgos zhes bka' stsal ba la brten sems nyid ngal
NK125(co)004:305: bso'i gzhung blo la zin te 'grel pa la blta
NK125(co)004:307: 'dul ba'i spyi don lung rigs gter mdzod las /
NK125(co)004:309: ma thob bar thob par byed pa'i gzhi dang /
NK125(co)004:311: gzhi gsum gyi bshad pa rnams har bton gyi blo
NK125(co)004:312: la zin nas bsam pas bskyangs pas go ba thal
NK125(co)004:313: thol skyes shing dper blo spro bar gyur pas da
NK125(co)004:314: ni rang gi 'dun byung thams cad thos bsam sgom
NK125(co)004:315: gsum la 'dril ba ma gtogs gzhan gnas skabs kyi
NK125(co)004:316: 'du 'dzi'i bya ba gang la'ang snying po mi 'dug
NK125(co)004:317: snyam pa'i dad 'dun cung zad skyes te /
NK125(co)004:318: rje bla ma dam pa pho brang chen por bzhugs
NK125(co)004:319: pa la snyan ngag gi zhu yig tshigs bcad dang
NK125(co)004:320: bcad pas klog pa'i grwa sar 'gro ba dang /
NK125(co)004:321: gzhis rang du thos bsam byed pa gang du rung ngam /
NK125(co)004:322: yang na sgom chig sgril byed pa ste /
NK125(co)004:323: don tshan gsum po gang la 'bad na phan rlabs
NK125(co)004:324: che zhes lung bstan zhus pa'i lan du 'di skad
NK125(co)004:325: ces stsal te / ngag la dbang ba skad gnyis smra ba'i sde /
NK125(co)004:326: chos tshul rgya mtsho'i dpal la longs spyod pa'i //
NK125(co)004:327: skal bzang de yi dri lan gsang po'i gtam //
NK125(co)004:328: brjod pa gang 'di thugs kyi bum par bstim //
NK125(co)004:329: deng dus skye bo phal cher 'dod yon la //
NK125(co)004:330: sred pas thos bsam sgom pa ring dor nas //
NK125(co)004:331: log 'tsho'i 'dam bur dga' bas rol na yang //
NK125(co)004:332: mkhas khyod 'dam skyes pad+mo ji bzhin nges //
NK125(co)004:333: rgyal bas gsungs pa'i chos tshul ji snyed don //
NK125(co)004:334: rang bloos theg na stobs su ma gyur pa //
NK125(co)004:335: med mod 'on kyang the tshom d+r+wa ba'i gzeb //
NK125(co)004:336: dam por yid gnyis ne tsho chud pa bzhin //
NK125(co)004:337: deng dus snga 'gyur bstan pa'i byin rlabs rgyun //
NK125(co)004:338: nyams pa med kyang bshad pa'i dga' ston la //
NK125(co)004:339: spyod nus thun mtshams nyid byed ltar gyur pa //
NK125(co)004:340: snying stobs zla ba'i 'od kyi gsal bya'i dus //
NK125(co)004:341: de phyir bslu med dkon mchog rnam gsum la //
NK125(co)004:342: brtags pa phul bar snying stobs bskyed pa'i don //
NK125(co)004:343: gegs med 'grub pa'i mtshan ma bzang mthong bas //
NK125(co)004:344: smon pa'i gnas rnams sgrub la brtson par mdzod //
NK125(co)004:345: snga 'gyur lam gyi bskyed bzlas rim pa rnams //
NK125(co)004:346: chag med bar chad zhi phyir 'bad pa gang //
NK125(co)004:347: da lta nyid bzhin g.yel ba med pa nas //
NK125(co)004:348: rim gro'i rnam pa phyis gsal bzhin du sgrubs //
NK125(co)004:349: thos pa'i rtsa ba chos mngon mdzod nyid dang //
NK125(co)004:350: sgyu 'phrul rtsa rgyud gsang ba snying po la //
NK125(co)004:351: rtsa pod byas nas shes bya gzhan la yang //
NK125(co)004:352: 'bad pas bsgrub na mkhas pa'i gnas thob 'gyur //
NK125(co)004:353: de mthus snga 'gyur bstan pa'i bshad sgrub nyid //
NK125(co)004:354: rab 'byams phan bde'i mkha' la rtag 'char ba'i //
NK125(co)004:355: rnam dpyod shing rta chen po khyod las gzhan //
NK125(co)004:356: re ba med pas the tshom mi bya'o //
NK125(co)004:357: rim gror dkon mchog mchod cing skongs bshags dang //
NK125(co)004:358: chos srung rnams la gsol mchod gu ru yi //
NK125(co)004:359: gsol 'debs bsam pa lhun grub stong tsho bsags //
NK125(co)004:360: de yis bkra shis bsam don thams cad 'grub //
NK125(co)004:361: ces gnang ba'i rim gro rnams tshes bco lnga'i dus
NK125(co)004:362: tshod thog grwa tshang la mang ja spong dag bcas
NK125(co)004:363: bsgrubs shing rang nyid kyis kyang bdun phrag gnyis kyi
NK125(co)004:364: bar du mtshams dam par bcad nas bsags rting /
NK125(co)004:365: rje gter chen chos kyi rgyal po'i drung du snying po'i 'grel pa par bkab dang /
NK125(co)004:366: g.yung t+aika sbyar ba'i steng nas gsung bshad zhus te /
NK125(co)004:367: g.yung t+aika blo 'dzin dang bstun bya ba gzhan khyad du bsad de /
NK125(co)004:368: gal che shos bsam pa'i shes rab la byas nas
NK125(co)004:369: legs par brtags pas rang shes rab kyi rtsal chung
NK125(co)004:371: bla ma dam pa'i byin rlabs kyi 'pho ba dang
NK125(co)004:372: legs bshad kyi gsung gis rang rgyud mi shes pa'i
NK125(co)004:373: mdud pa dkrol te ring por ma thogs par rgyud
NK125(co)004:374: kyi dngos sbas kyi don thams cad i thi ba
NK125(co)004:375: longs pa'i go ba rnyed cing /
NK125(co)004:376: chos mngon pa mdzod kyi bshad pa ni gzhung lugs
NK125(co)004:377: rab 'byams smra ba sangs rgyas chos dar la gzhung
NK125(co)004:378: brgya pa'i t+ai ka'i thog nas tshar gcig nyan na'ang
NK125(co)004:379: / bye mdo'i chos skad 'di klog pa'i grwa sa
NK125(co)004:380: rnams su'ang ha cang dar chung bas 'bel gtam smra
NK125(co)004:381: ba nyung ba bcas rtsa pod kyi blo la sims
NK125(co)004:382: thim pa zhig ma byung yang bag chags 'jog byed
NK125(co)004:383: / tsam dang / de bzhin du snga phyi ci
NK125(co)004:384: rigs par lung rig gter mdzod dang rgya mtsho'i steng
NK125(co)004:385: nas 'dul ba dang phar phyin gyi bshad pa'ang yam
NK125(co)004:386: tsam zhig nyan te bsam pa'i rtog dpyod kyis legs
NK125(co)004:387: par bskyangs pas go ba'i phyogs 'go things pa tsam
NK125(co)004:388: / tsam dang / byas / de'i gong du gong thang pan chen las dbu ma'i stong thun dang /
NK125(co)004:389: 'dul ba sum brgya pa'i bshad pa /
NK125(co)004:390: mkhas grub chos skyong rgyal mtshan la rang 'grel gyi
NK125(co)004:391: steng nas zab mo nang don gyi bshad pa rnams
NK125(co)004:392: thos / khyad par rje bla ma dam pa'i drung du kun mkhyen dri med 'od zer /
NK125(co)004:394: rong zom chen po la sogs pa'i gsung rab rnams
NK125(co)004:395: re re nas bshad pa thun du bcug ste nyan
NK125(co)004:397: dka' gnas rnams la dri ba'i phra gcod dang /
NK125(co)004:398: rgyun du rang bzhin gyi gsung 'phros tsam yang gdams
NK125(co)004:399: par 'bebs pa'i gnad kyis 'bel gtam mang du thos
NK125(co)004:401: thos bsam gang byas kha phyir bltas su ma song
NK125(co)004:402: bar rgyud thog tu bsgril thub pa'i bka' drin thob
NK125(co)004:403: pa yin no // da ni rgyal ba'i bka' dang
NK125(co)004:404: dgongs 'grel gyi bstan bcos smin grol gyi lam ston
NK125(co)004:405: pa'i man ngag du ma'i bka' lung ji ltar thob
NK125(co)004:406: pa yin no // pa'i tshul ni / gtso bor
NK125(co)004:407: bka' drin 'gran zla dang bral ba rje bla ma
NK125(co)004:408: dam pa gter chen chos kyi rgyal po'i zhabs pad
NK125(co)004:409: rtag tu spyi bor bsnyen te legs par thob pa
NK125(co)004:410: pa yin no // pa'i tshul ni / la / snga 'gyur bka' ma mdo sgyu sems gsum /
NK125(co)004:411: sems phyogs la'ang sems klong man ngag gi sde gsum /
NK125(co)004:412: de dag dang rjes 'brel dong sprug sogs rgyud sde'i
NK125(co)004:413: skor gyi dbang bka' bshad lung man ngag gi bka'
NK125(co)004:414: brgyud lugs tha dad pa du ma dang bcas pa
NK125(co)004:415: rgyun bzhugs so cog lta bu dang /
NK125(co)004:416: sgrub sde la spyi bka' dang /
NK125(co)004:417: sgos bka' yang phur gshin rje gshed kyi skor so
NK125(co)004:418: so la'ang nang gses kyi khyad par du ma dang
NK125(co)004:419: bcas pa / gter ma'i skor la /
NK125(co)004:420: rje nyid kyi gter gsar yongs rdzogs /
NK125(co)004:421: gzhan ma grub thob dngos grub /
NK125(co)004:431: byang gter snga phyi sogs grags che ba'i gter ston
NK125(co)004:432: mang po zhig gi gter chos bla rdzogs thugs gsum
NK125(co)004:433: / bka' brgyad spyi sgos kyi skor mtha' yas pa dang /
NK125(co)004:434: kun mkhyen lnga pa chen po'i rgya can gyi mtshon
NK125(co)004:435: zab mo dag snang ma'i skor sogs snga 'gyur gsang
NK125(co)004:436: sngags rnying ma'i lugs kyi dbang lung mang po dang
NK125(co)004:437: / man ngag gi bka' ci rigs pa bcas pa /
NK125(co)004:438: de thams cad kyi rtsa bar gyur pa rnying ma rgyud 'bum gyi lung yongs rdzogs /
NK125(co)004:441: mi 'khrugs pa sogs kyi dbang rjes gnang mang po dang /
NK125(co)004:442: n+aa ro mkha' spyod kyi mtshon pa'i dbang lung man ngag tshang ba mang po zhig dang /
NK125(co)004:443: mdo'i skor la'ang srol gnyis kyi sems bskyed gdams ngag dang bcas pa dang /
NK125(co)004:444: byang sa'i lung la sogs pa dang /
NK125(co)004:445: mdo sngags spyi yi bshad chos kun mkhyen klong chen
NK125(co)004:446: pa'i bstan bcos sogs rgya bod kyi gzhung man ngag
NK125(co)004:447: mang po'i bka' lung yang bka' drin du thob cing
NK125(co)004:448: / gzhan yang rdo rje brag rig 'dzin mchog gi
NK125(co)004:449: sprul pa'i skur dus 'khor yongs rdzogs kyi dbang dang
NK125(co)004:451: bla ma gsang 'dus kyi rtsal dbang dang gza' dbang sogs /
NK125(co)004:452: dpal sa skya ba bdag chen kun dga' bkra shis la'ang yang dag 'khon lugs kyi dbang dang /
NK125(co)004:454: rgyal sras pad+ma 'gyur med rgya mtshor mnyam sbyor rigs bsdus kyi dbang dang /
NK125(co)004:455: byang chub lam rim gyi khrid /
NK125(co)004:456: deng ri kun spangs blo gros brtan pa la zhi
NK125(co)004:457: byed snga phyi bar gsum kha thor dang bcas pa'i
NK125(co)004:458: dbang lung khrid gsum yongs rdzogs dang /
NK125(co)004:460: mkhas grub chos skyong rgyal mtshan la shangs lugs kyi dbang man ngag tshang ma dang /
NK125(co)004:462: rat+na b+ha dra nas brgyud pa'i dus 'khor gyi dbang gong ma dang sbyor drug gi shar khrid /
NK125(co)004:463: shes rab kyi lha drug gi rjes gnang /
NK125(co)004:464: spyan ras gzigs dpal mo lugs dang /
NK125(co)004:470: le lag zab don skor sogs /
NK125(co)004:471: mus thang gong ma grub pa'i dbang phyug blo gros
NK125(co)004:472: rgya mtsho la dus 'khor gyi dbang yongs rdzogs dang
NK125(co)004:475: shangs lugs kyi khrid yig gi skor /
NK125(co)004:476: jo lugs 'jigs byed kyi dbang sogs dbang rjes gnang lung mang po /
NK125(co)004:477: mkhas btsun ngag dbang bstan 'dzin la rdo rje phreng ba'i dbang sogs /
NK125(co)004:478: rdo rje 'dzin pa kun dga' bstan pa dar rgyas la gsang bde 'jigs gsum /
NK125(co)004:479: rngogs lugs kyi gur rigs bsdus gdan bzhi ma h+aa ma ya rnams dang /
NK125(co)004:484: bshes gnyen byams pa phun tshogs rnams rgyal la spyan ras gzigs sed+ge'i sgra /
NK125(co)004:486: bsrung ba'i mkhar gtum chung khra thogs /
NK125(co)004:487: grwa pa'i gtum chung dmar po /
NK125(co)004:488: 'gro bzang lugs rnam sras dkar po tshe 'dzin /
NK125(co)004:489: spyan ras gzigs dpal mo lugs /
NK125(co)004:490: gur zhal rnams kyi rjes gnang /
NK125(co)004:491: sdom brtson kun dga' dar rgyas la 'dul ba me tog phreng rgyud /
NK125(co)004:496: jo bo'i chos chung brgya rtsa rnams kyi lung /
NK125(co)004:497: lung dang rig pa'i dbang phyug sangs rgyas chos dar la dbu ma rtsa 'jug /
NK125(co)004:502: sa pan gyi thub pa dgongs gsal /
NK125(co)004:503: lung rigs gter mdzod rnams kyi lung /
NK125(co)004:504: skyi kun dga' bstan gsal la sgyu 'phrul phra mo'i
NK125(co)004:505: skor mang po dang zur tsho stod lugs pa'i sgyu
NK125(co)004:507: grub chen kun bzang chos rgyal la rog pa'i mtshan dpe /
NK125(co)004:508: grub pa'i dbang phyug dam pa klong yangs 'od gsal la rog phur sogs /
NK125(co)004:509: 'bras bu gling pa ngag dbang o rgyan la mnyam sbyor rigs bsdus kyi dbang /
NK125(co)004:510: zhwa lu byang ma pa rin po che bzang por dri med rnam gnyis kyi dbang lung /
NK125(co)004:511: thugs sras sprul pa'i skur tshe khrid rdor phreng gi dbang rgyas dang /
NK125(co)004:513: rta mgrin yang gsang bla med kyi dbang /
NK125(co)004:514: bka' 'gyur ba grub pa rdo rje la 'dul ba lung /
NK125(co)004:517: nges don gyi mdzod phran sogs dang /
NK125(co)004:519: spyod 'jug la sogs pa nyer mkho mang po'i lung /
NK125(co)004:520: 'bri gung sprul pa'i skur sgra mi snyan pa'i tshe dbang /
NK125(co)004:521: kre bo sprul pa'i sku chos kyi dbang por kar
NK125(co)004:522: lugs kyi phyag chen lhan cig skyes sbyor gyi khrid
NK125(co)004:523: dang / dbang phyug rdo rjes mdzad pa'i khrid yig rgyas pa dang /
NK125(co)004:524: pe har gyi sgrub thabs sprin nag 'khrigs pa'i lung /
NK125(co)004:525: dpa' bo sprul pa'i skur phyag chen yi ge bzhi pa'i don tshigs bcad ma'i lung rnams zhus shing /
NK125(co)004:526: de dag kyang dus gang gi tshe bshes gnyen gang
NK125(co)004:527: las chos bka' gang dang gang thob pa'i tho byang
NK125(co)004:528: gi yi ge logs su yod pas 'dir rgyas pa
NK125(co)004:529: ma spros so // bzhi pa ji ltar thob pa'i don nyams su cung zad blang tshul ni /
NK125(co)004:530: spyir thos bsam gyi sgro 'dogs bcad pa'i don rnams
NK125(co)004:531: blang dor gyi sgo nas sgrub cing nyams su len
NK125(co)004:533: 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs bsam zhing mi rtag 'chi ba
NK125(co)004:534: dran pa'i skyo shas kyis bskul te dkon mchog kun
NK125(co)004:535: 'dus bla ma dam pa la sems rnyog pa med
NK125(co)004:536: par dang ba'i dad pa dang /
NK125(co)004:537: las 'bras mi bslu bar yid ches kyi dad pa dang /
NK125(co)004:538: gzhan don bla med byang chub thob 'dod skom pa
NK125(co)004:539: chu la gdung ba lta bu 'dod pa'i dad pa
NK125(co)004:540: ste / de ltar dad pa gsum gyis yid dam pa'i chos la 'dun pa'i sgo nas /
NK125(co)004:541: bsam pa'i go gyon zhing sbyor bas dge ba sgrub par 'jug pa'i brtson 'grus dang /
NK125(co)004:542: dge ba'i sems kyi dmigs yul dang blang dor mi brjed pa'i dran pa dang /
NK125(co)004:543: dmigs yul las gzhan du mi g.yengs pa'i ting 'dzin dang /
NK125(co)004:544: chos thams cad sgyu ma lta bur shes pa'i shes
NK125(co)004:545: rab rnams ci tshang gis nyams su len pa la
NK125(co)004:546: spro ba brtas par bgyis shing /
NK125(co)004:547: khyad par rang lo nyer bdun pa lcags spre'i lo
NK125(co)004:548: la kre bo sprul pa'i sku dang mnyam du rje
NK125(co)004:549: bla ma dam pa la rig 'dzin thugs tig gi
NK125(co)004:550: bka' khrid zhus te legs par bsgoms pas /
NK125(co)004:551: rnam rtog ri gzar gyi 'ba' chu lta bus sgom
NK125(co)004:552: rang mi skye ba 'dra snyam ma'i gu dog gi
NK125(co)004:553: blo tsa ba tsub ci drag langs par gyur pa
NK125(co)004:554: phyis bltas na rnam rtog ngo shes kyi nyams kyi
NK125(co)004:556: ngo sprad kyi zhal ta zhu nus pa ma byung /
NK125(co)004:557: de steng shing pho byi ba'i lo bya rgod pa
NK125(co)004:558: chos skyong rgyal mtshan la ni gu chos drug gi
NK125(co)004:559: khrid dang / ding ri ba blo gros brtan par
NK125(co)004:560: zhi byed bka' babs gsum gyi khrid tshang ma dang
NK125(co)004:561: khrid dang / / khyad par so khrid dang lam
NK125(co)004:562: lnga'i nang nas tshogs lam gyi khrid nyams su bskyangs
NK125(co)004:563: khrid dang / / lo byas / me stag lor
NK125(co)004:564: chos skyong rgyal mtshan slar yang dgon par phebs par
NK125(co)004:565: phyag rgya chen po ga'u ma'i khrid zhus nas 'bad
NK125(co)004:566: pa chen pos mtshams bcad de bsgoms pas zhi gnas
NK125(co)004:568: lo de kha'i mjug tu chos skyong rgyal mtshan dang
NK125(co)004:569: mnyam du rje bla ma dam pa'i drung du thugs
NK125(co)004:570: rje chen po bde gshegs kun 'dus kyi khrid ma
NK125(co)004:572: khyad par rtsa khrid la snying rus bskyed nas bsgoms
NK125(co)004:573: pas rdzogs rim rdo rje'i lus la gnad du bsnun
NK125(co)004:574: pa'i byed bcings kyis rtsa rlung thig le dbu mar
NK125(co)004:575: dwangs pa'i lag rjes stong gzugs kyi rnam pa bde
NK125(co)004:576: stong gi rol mor 'char bar bshad pa ltar mi
NK125(co)004:577: g.yo gsum ldan gyis btsan thabs kyi gnad la brten
NK125(co)004:579: rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong gzugs rang rig dang
NK125(co)004:580: dbyer med du rtogs pa'i nyams myong la sim pa
NK125(co)004:581: thob pa zhig ma mchis rung /
NK125(co)004:582: rdzogs rim gyi gnad rang rig ka dag gi gshis lugs 'gyur med spros bral dang /
NK125(co)004:583: de'i rtsal snang chos kun ris med sgyu ma lta
NK125(co)004:584: bu'i rol pa ma 'gag pas don la snang rig
NK125(co)004:585: ngos bzung dang bral ba la go ba'i nges shes
NK125(co)004:586: brtan po rnyed de snang ba rang ga ma'i bden
NK125(co)004:587: zhen gyi 'khri ba dam sgrim me ba la nan
NK125(co)004:588: btsir byed dgos pa rang ma mchis tsam dang /
NK125(co)004:589: sgyu 'dra'i 'khor ba sgyu ma lta bu'i sdug bsngal
NK125(co)004:590: la spyod pa'i sems can rnams la des drangs pa'i
NK125(co)004:591: dmigs med kyi snying rje'i 'char sgo yang rkyen la
NK125(co)004:592: brten nas sad sud 'char 'char 'dra ba sogs snang
NK125(co)004:593: yang go ba tsam las nyams myong dang rtogs pas
NK125(co)004:594: phu thag chod pa zhig dka' bar mchis kyang lta
NK125(co)004:595: sgom spyod gsum 'bras bu bla na med pa'i byang
NK125(co)004:596: chub kyi rgyur 'gor mi 'gro'i gnad kyis blang dor
NK125(co)004:597: gyi tshul cung zad nges so //
NK125(co)004:598: phyis su'ang rje bla ma dam pa las snying thig rnam gnyis dang /
NK125(co)004:600: a ti zab don snying po /
NK125(co)004:601: rdor sems kyi khrid ma bu /
NK125(co)004:602: klong sde rdo rje zam pa /
NK125(co)004:604: khros nag gcod khrid sogs bka' gter gyi zab khrid mang du nod cing /
NK125(co)004:605: re re nas nyams len la brtson pa byed blo
NK125(co)004:606: byas bas rang blo dang 'tshams par bogs cung zad
NK125(co)004:608: de las gzhan du grub pa'i dbang phyug blo gros
NK125(co)004:609: rgyal mtshan la sbyor drug gi sor sdud nyin mtshan
NK125(co)004:610: gyi rnal 'byor tsam zhig nyams khrid du thob cing
NK125(co)004:611: / dam po 'debs pa'ang lag len du btab mod /
NK125(co)004:612: 'char sgo rang gi rtsal ha cang che ba byung /
NK125(co)004:613: gang lta yang rang snying rus chung bas /
NK125(co)004:614: sgom dang gang zag ya bral du song ba ma
NK125(co)004:615: gtogs bla ma dam pa rnams kyi bka' drin gyis
NK125(co)004:616: zab lam gyi gnad rnams nyams 'og tu chub pa'i
NK125(co)004:617: nges shes cung zad thob pa yin no //
NK125(co)004:618: de bzhin du rgyal bas gsungs pa'i cho ga bzhin
NK125(co)004:619: du rang 'bras kyi khyad par sngags mthu'i nus pa
NK125(co)004:620: dang / ngo bo zhu bde'i bde stong gi rang bzhin /
NK125(co)004:621: byed las dag rdzogs smin gsum tshang ba ste /
NK125(co)004:622: khyad par bzhi ldan gyi bskyed rim gyi gnad la'ang /
NK125(co)004:623: go ba tsam skyes pa ltar mos sgom gyis slob lam bgyis shing /
NK125(co)004:624: de'i thun mtshams kyi rnal 'byor dang 'brel ba'i bzlas brjod kyang /
NK125(co)004:625: shing pho khyi'i lor mkha' spyod bde chen gling du
NK125(co)004:626: mtshams zla ba lnga lhag tsam zhig bcad bde gshegs
NK125(co)004:627: kun 'dus kyi phyi nang gsang gsum gyi bsnyen sgrub
NK125(co)004:628: smin par byas shing de nas bzung ste phyi sgrub
NK125(co)004:629: kyi rgyun bzlas kyang stong phrag re ma chag par
NK125(co)004:630: bgyis pas khyon bsdoms kyi grangs sngon 'gro'i skyabs 'gro
NK125(co)004:631: bdun khri / sems bskyed drug khri dgu stong /
NK125(co)004:632: yig brgya 'bum drug stong lnga brgya /
NK125(co)004:634: yan lag bdun pa dang gsol 'debs drug khri bzhi stong dgu brgya rnams dang /
NK125(co)004:635: yig bcu'i ngag bzlas bye ba brgyad sa ya drug
NK125(co)004:636: 'bu ma tsho brgyad kha longs ba dang bcas pa
NK125(co)004:637: / yid bzlas lnga khri sum stong brgal tsam /
NK125(co)004:638: rta yum gnyis re rer brgyad 'bum chig khri /
NK125(co)004:640: byin bsdu drug khri dgu stong /
NK125(co)004:641: phyi sgrub dang sbyar ba'i rdor bzlas nyis 'bum brgyad khri bdun stong rnams bzlas /
NK125(co)004:642: de bzhin du thugs thig gi sngon 'gro'i yig brgya drug khri lnga brgya lhag tsam dang /
NK125(co)004:643: phyi sgrub kyi bzlas pa sa ya gcig bzhi 'bum drug khri dgu stong /
NK125(co)004:644: sgyu 'phrul zhi ba phyag rgya gcig pa'i yab yum gyi sngags so sor drug khri nyis stong dang /
NK125(co)004:645: spyi sngags drug khri lnga stong /
NK125(co)004:646: 'dus pa mdo'i spyi sngags chig 'bum drug khri /
NK125(co)004:647: ma ti lugs kyi 'jam dkar la lnga 'bum bzhi khri /
NK125(co)004:648: rta nag lcags ral can la 'bum phrag bcu gsum lhag bcas /
NK125(co)004:649: nyang gi khros nag la 'bum phrag gsum /
NK125(co)004:650: phag dkar shes rab gsal byed la 'bum tsho lnga /
NK125(co)004:651: dbyangs can ma dkar mo sum 'bum /
NK125(co)004:652: na rag dong sprugs kyi yig brgya chig khri /
NK125(co)004:653: bka' brgyad gtso dgu dang shangs lugs rgyud sde lnga la 'ang 'brel pa tsam re bzlas te /
NK125(co)004:654: de rnams shing bya yan chad las kyi rnam g.yeng gis chag cing /
NK125(co)004:655: da lta'i chu sprul zla ba drug pa'i tshes bcu
NK125(co)004:656: yan chad la chag med bzlas pa'i grangs thugs rje
NK125(co)004:657: chen po sngar song ba ltar dang /
NK125(co)004:658: gzhan yang gar dbang tshe dpag med kyi phyi sgyub kyi bzlas pa sum 'bum sum khri /
NK125(co)004:659: tshe dpag med yang snying kun 'dus kyi bzlas pa sa ya gcig dang bzhi khri /
NK125(co)004:660: bla ma drag por sum 'bum kha longs bcas /
NK125(co)004:661: rdor sems kyi yig drug sum 'bum dang /
NK125(co)004:663: zhi byed tshogs lam bzlas pa sa ya gcig chig 'bum /
NK125(co)004:665: rjes dang ro snyoms gnyis la chig 'bum re /
NK125(co)004:666: byad grol la brgyad khri tsam zhig dang /
NK125(co)004:667: gshin rje 'joms byed kyi sngags tshan bzhi yang 'brel
NK125(co)004:668: ba tsam zhig bzlas pa sogs nyung sbrel gyi mtshams
NK125(co)004:669: dang rgyun bzlas chag med srol du bcug ste dkar
NK125(co)004:670: po'i las kyi bag chags kun gzhi la cung zad
NK125(co)004:671: bzhag / gzhan yang yos lo'i nang du rlung 'thems
NK125(co)004:672: pa'i 'chi ltas gsal bar rdor bzlas 'bum khri gsum
NK125(co)004:673: bzlas pas sor chud bar gyur cing /
NK125(co)004:674: shing bya lor bde gshegs kun 'dus kyi khrid mtshams
NK125(co)004:675: dang sbyar bas rdor bzlas chig 'bum bdun khri dgu
NK125(co)004:676: stong bzlas pa la'ang rtags mtshan legs par gtogs pa
NK125(co)004:678: nyin zhag phrugs rer thun drug gsol 'debs /
NK125(co)004:679: zhog pa chu sbyin dzam lha dkar cha bzhi /
NK125(co)004:683: gzhi bdag dang brtan gtor kha 'bar ma dkar mo'i gtor ma rnams dang /
NK125(co)004:684: de rjes dbu ma lugs kyi sems bskyed dang sngags sdom bzung zhing /
NK125(co)004:685: rnam 'joms ltung bshags sogs kha ton ci rigs dang /
NK125(co)004:688: nyin par blta rtog rtsom pa /
NK125(co)004:690: snga gung chag med kyi rgyun bzlas rnam dang /
NK125(co)004:691: rlung sbyor sogs dus gnad dmigs su gang 'gro'i dge sbyor /
NK125(co)004:692: mtshan mo dam can spyi gtor rjes 'brang dang bcas pa'i steng sgos su drag po sde lnga /
NK125(co)004:695: dur khrod ma mo rnams kyi gtor chog /
NK125(co)004:700: mkha' 'gro spyi gtor bcas gtor bsngosa rim pa dang /
NK125(co)004:701: dkar 'gyed dang 'chi bslu'i dmigs pa ste /
NK125(co)004:702: nang nub nyal ldang gi rnal 'byor mtshan bcas mtshan
NK125(co)004:703: med gang bde re la sgrigs su chub par bgyis
NK125(co)004:704: so // mdor na mnyam bzhag rnam par mi rtog
NK125(co)004:705: pa'i ye shes rang bzhin babs kyi bsam gtan gyi
NK125(co)004:707: de ltar ma rtogs pa la dmigs med kyi snying
NK125(co)004:708: rje chen po'i rtsal snang lhar skur langs te res
NK125(co)004:709: 'ga' de'i ngang la 'jog pa rnams ci rigs su
NK125(co)004:710: sgom zhing / rjes shes kyi gnas skabs kun tu
NK125(co)004:711: shes bzhin gyi dran pas ci sleb kyi gtso bor
NK125(co)004:712: skyabs kun 'dus kyi ngo bo bla ma dam par
NK125(co)004:713: re ltos bcas nas thugs ci zin dang ci mnyes
NK125(co)004:714: lhur len pas bka' lung las nam du'ang mi 'gong
NK125(co)004:716: bsam byung gi yon tan sngar shes rnams gong du
NK125(co)004:717: 'gyur ci thon gyi 'bad rtsol nan chag pa dang
NK125(co)004:718: / sngar 'dris kyi mi la gzhung bzang gis mi
NK125(co)004:719: byol zhing phyis nas gsar 'grogs kyi ngo shes mang
NK125(co)004:721: rang gzhan grub mtha' dang bshes gnyen kun la dag
NK125(co)004:722: snang sbyong ci thub las phyogs ris kyi chags sdang
NK125(co)004:724: tshe 'dir ltos kyi snang ba la ha cang dngos
NK125(co)004:725: zhen che ba mi byed pa'i zhe dam gyis dus
NK125(co)004:726: rtag par bzo grwa mi chag pa sogs mthun rkyen
NK125(co)004:727: 'jom yang / ri mo tsakli re tsam yang 'brir
NK125(co)004:728: bskul ba sogs nyer mkho'i bzo phran mi 'chor bar
NK125(co)004:729: gang byung tsam gyi chog tsho zin pa bya ba
NK125(co)004:730: 'jom yang / dang / grwa rigs yon bdag kun
NK125(co)004:731: la nye 'gyang gi phyogs ris spang ste dbu ma'i
NK125(co)004:733: sger ltos kyi gang zag nyi tshe'i don la ru
NK125(co)004:734: gal gyi bshags dang bsnyen rdzogs bshad pa byed pa'i
NK125(co)004:735: zhu sne sbyor ba sogs bya byed mang po la
NK125(co)004:737: dge 'dun spyi dang 'brel ba'i slob grwa sgrigs gnon
NK125(co)004:738: sogs la rang nus pa zhan pas shogs thon pa
NK125(co)004:739: dka' yang lhag bsam bzang pos kha bcos 'gro ba
NK125(co)004:740: thams cad la bskul nas rang nus gang thon byed
NK125(co)004:741: pa dang / gzhis byed kyi bsngo rten dang 'bul
NK125(co)004:742: ba sogs gnyen phyag gang du 'gro ba'i dmigs gang
NK125(co)004:743: yin der blos gtsang gis stobs ste /
NK125(co)004:744: rang le lo can la bu lon du 'gyur ba'i nyer len las bsrung bar byas shing /
NK125(co)004:745: de ltar byas pas shing khyi'i lo tsam nas bzung
NK125(co)004:746: zhor byung gi yo byad kyang 'bad med du 'du
NK125(co)004:747: ba byung ste / lha'i bu'i bdud kyis mgo bskoor
NK125(co)004:748: ma yin par mchog gsum gyi thugs rje las byung
NK125(co)004:749: ba yin na 'tshengs par snang ngo //
NK125(co)004:750: lnga pa rang nus dang sbyar ba'i gzhan don cha tsam bsgrul tshul ni /
NK125(co)004:751: bstan pa spyi dang bye brag snga 'gyur rdo rje theg pa /
NK125(co)004:752: yang sgos rje gter chen bla ma'i bshad sgrub kyi
NK125(co)004:753: bstan pa rin po che 'di nyid sgo thams cad
NK125(co)004:754: nas phyogs kun tu dar zhing rgyas bar 'gyur na
NK125(co)004:755: ci ma rung snyam pa'i lhag bsam gyi snying stobs
NK125(co)004:757: 'chad nyan gyi gzugs brnyan rang nus gang thon gyi
NK125(co)004:758: byed blo bgyis par sgra ka l+aa pa'i me yan
NK125(co)004:759: gyi sa ris dang por dge slong thar pa gling
NK125(co)004:760: pa dang / de rjes bshes gnyen chags pa chos 'phel dang /
NK125(co)004:761: dge slong o rgyan dpal 'byor la bshad cing /
NK125(co)004:762: phyis sa ris yongs rdzogs dang /
NK125(co)004:763: snyan ngag sdeb sbyor gyi bshad pa rnams zhabs drung
NK125(co)004:764: rin po che la phul ba las kyang mang du
NK125(co)004:765: mched pas / dbyangs can b+y+aa ka ra na ni
NK125(co)004:766: zhabs drung sku mched sogs kyis dbus tshar lnga tsam
NK125(co)004:767: mched pas / bshad / rtsis kyi sam ris thun
NK125(co)004:768: du bcug nas rang gi dngos su bslab pa med
NK125(co)004:769: mched pas / bshad / kyang / sngar shes zin
NK125(co)004:770: la 'phral gyi 'bel gtam mtha' dpyod kyi blo kha
NK125(co)004:771: phye ste brgyud nas phan par byung bas tha snyad
NK125(co)004:772: kyi rigs gnas rnams la'ang gzhan don gyi 'brel ba
NK125(co)004:773: tsam bzhag cing gtso bor mkhan po'i g.yar khral blangs
NK125(co)004:774: pas sdom pa bgyis pa'i sdom phrug gi grangs dge
NK125(co)004:775: slong bzhi brgya dang zhe bdun /
NK125(co)004:776: dge tshul chig stong nyis brgya go brgyad du longs pa dang /
NK125(co)004:777: grwa gtsang gi dbyar dgun gyi chos thob gnyis la
NK125(co)004:778: lcags sbrul nas brtsams te zhabs drung sku mched dang
NK125(co)004:779: phyogs kyi bla khag mang po grwa gtsang gi grwa
NK125(co)004:780: pa don gnyer can 'dus pa drug cu skor te
NK125(co)004:781: snying po'i rgyud kyi bshad pa chag med kyi blo
NK125(co)004:782: gsar rnams la thos byung gi shes rab bskyed par
NK125(co)004:783: byas shing gzhan yang so so'i blo dang 'tshams pa'i
NK125(co)004:786: 'dul ba sogs gzhung so so'i bshad pa tho re ba dang /
NK125(co)004:787: snga phyir gsung sprul rim po che ngag dbang kun bzang rdo rje /
NK125(co)004:788: dpal ri sprul pa'i sku thang 'brog sprul pa'i sku /
NK125(co)004:789: zang la mkhar sprul pa'i sku /
NK125(co)004:791: rong pa rdzogs chen sprul pa'i sku rnams dang /
NK125(co)004:792: rna bo gdung brgyud sogs kyi mtshon gzhi byes kyi
NK125(co)004:793: don gnyer can mang po la sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i
NK125(co)004:794: dbang tshar brgyad / mdor dbang tshar gsum /
NK125(co)004:795: bde 'dus kyi dbang chen tshar gcig dang /
NK125(co)004:800: rdor gling rat+na gling pa pad gling gi gter chos
NK125(co)004:801: sogs bka' gter gyi dbang rjes gnang mang po dang
NK125(co)004:802: / bklag lung man ngag gi khrid 'bogs pa sogs gang la gang 'tshams kyi chos 'chad pa dang /
NK125(co)004:805: shangs lugs rgyud sde lnga sogs dbang bka' che chung dang /
NK125(co)004:806: khrid chen lnga sogs dbang rjes gnang zab khrid lung dang bcas pa mang du byas shing /
NK125(co)004:807: phyis su'ang khyi lo gram pa dpal gyi sa skyar phyin te /
NK125(co)004:808: bdag chen 'jam dpal dbyangs ngag dbang kun dga' bkra
NK125(co)004:809: shis kyi zhabs drung du gter gsar yongs rdzogs kyi
NK125(co)004:810: dbang lung dang / thugs rje chen po'i smin khrid /
NK125(co)004:812: g.yu thog snying thig dbang lung dang thugs sgyub kyi dbang /
NK125(co)004:814: lo k+t+ri rjes gnang gnod sbyin gyi srog gtad sogs
NK125(co)004:815: chos skyes mang po dang byad 'grel rnams phul zhing
NK125(co)004:816: de dus yar lam yar 'brog gling du zhabs drung
NK125(co)004:817: yab sras la tshe gur rta mgrin lok+t+ri rnams kyi
NK125(co)004:818: dbang dang / mar lam ru lag rgyang du bla ma za lung ba /
NK125(co)004:820: bsam gtan 'bras khud pa rnams la gter gsar bla ma zhi drag /
NK125(co)004:821: rdor sems a don rnams kyi dbang /
NK125(co)004:822: phun tshogs gling du dge slong 'byung gnas la phyag drug pa dang /
NK125(co)004:824: gzhis kha rtser smon grub nas la tshe gur rta mgrin rnams kyi dbang dang byad 'grol /
NK125(co)004:825: gsang sngags gling gdung rgyud mched la dong sprugs pad+ma brgya ldan gyi dbang dang /
NK125(co)004:826: dpon slob thun mong la tshe dbang /
NK125(co)004:827: 'o yug tu bsam dar nas la tshe gur dang zhang blon gyi rjes gnang yul par khrom dbang /
NK125(co)004:828: stag snar kre bo sprul pa'i sku la sgyu 'phrul zhi khro dang /
NK125(co)004:829: sems sde a don gyi dbang /
NK125(co)004:831: thugs rje chen po'i khrid yig gi lung dang shar khrid bcas phul /
NK125(co)004:832: gzhan yang snga phyir lho brag ban pa bsam 'grub dgon du dong sprugs kyi dbang dang /
NK125(co)004:833: tshe gur rta nag lcags ral can rnams kyi dbang /
NK125(co)004:834: dge yer khrom dbang dang tshe gur /
NK125(co)004:835: mdo mkhar du tshe gur rta mgrin /
NK125(co)004:836: dwags po rtse ler gur drag /
NK125(co)004:838: tshe rta rnams kyi rjes gnang dang /
NK125(co)004:842: zang ri o rgyan gling grwa tshang gi tshogs su na rag dong sprugs /
NK125(co)004:848: rgyal po rnams kyi srog gtad /
NK125(co)004:849: pad gling gter chos tshang ma'i lung dang /
NK125(co)004:850: bla ma'i las byang lha khrid kyi lha khrid /
NK125(co)004:852: ph+y+wa 'phrin mdos bcu sogs chog phran mang po'i lung rnams byas /
NK125(co)004:853: gzhis su rang gi ma rin po che la rje
NK125(co)004:854: bla ma'i bka' bzhin phyag chen gwa'u ma'i nyams khrid
NK125(co)004:856: thugs rje chen po yi ge drug ma'i lha khrid rnams phul zhing /
NK125(co)004:857: sku gshegs rting gdung mchod du bsdad nas sgrib sbyongs kyi cho ga gnad du gang 'gro zhus /
NK125(co)004:858: na ning chu 'brug gi lo la mdo khams kyi
NK125(co)004:859: sa'i thig le chab mdo byam pa gling du phyin
NK125(co)004:860: te / 'jig rten dbang phyug 'phags pa rgyal ba
NK125(co)004:861: rgya mtsho'i zhal snga nas dang zhabs phyir sprul sku
NK125(co)004:862: rnams gnyis bcas par gter gsar thugs rje chen po'i
NK125(co)004:863: rtsal dbang dang tshe dbang thugs thig gi rtsa dbang
NK125(co)004:864: te / / 'chi med yang snying kun 'dus kyi tshe dbang brgya rtsa /
NK125(co)004:865: rdor sems gur drag 'joms byed rnams kyi dbang /
NK125(co)004:866: gter rnying las gsang 'dus zlum po bzhi dbang /
NK125(co)004:867: nyang gi drag dmar che ba phyag rdor dregs 'dul gyi dbang che chung /
NK125(co)004:869: khang brtsegs rta mgrin gsang sgrub /
NK125(co)004:872: na rag dong sprugs zhi khro khrom sprugs lugs kyi dbang rjes gnang /
NK125(co)004:877: thugs rje chen po dang yang thig gi 'chi bslu sogs sku rim yang mang du bsgrub /
NK125(co)004:878: thugs kyi sras ngag dbang mchog gi sprul pa'i sku
NK125(co)004:879: la'ang gter gsar skor gyi dbang lung khrid dang bcas
NK125(co)004:881: rat+na gling pa'i phur pa dang zab lam gsang 'dus ma gtogs chos skor cha tshang /
NK125(co)004:882: 'jigs byed lha bcu gsum ma'i dbang dang bdun gyi lung /
NK125(co)004:883: n+aa ro mkha' spyod ma'i byin rlabs rnal 'byor bcu gcig dang rtsa dbu ma'i khrid /
NK125(co)004:885: thugs rje chen po rgyal po lugs kyi dbang khrid /
NK125(co)004:886: dpal mo lugs kyi rjes gnang dang /
NK125(co)004:888: bla ma gsang 'dus kyi rtsa dbang dang /
NK125(co)004:890: g.yu thog snying thig gi dbang le tshan rnams phul zhing /
NK125(co)004:891: phyag mdzod rje dpon rin po cher yang thugs rje chen po /
NK125(co)004:894: lok+t+ri rnams kyi dbang rjes gnang dang /
NK125(co)004:896: dbon po rnam gnyis sogs zhabs rim nang ma mang
NK125(co)004:897: por thugs thig gi dbang lung khrid dang bcas pa
NK125(co)004:899: gling pa dang nang ma'i grwa rigs mang por bla ma zhi drag /
NK125(co)004:902: tshe dbang mda' 'phel ma rnams kyi dbang dang /
NK125(co)004:905: tshe dpag med dwangs ma bcud 'dren gyi dbang /
NK125(co)004:906: 'khor ba dbyings sgrol dang sbyor drug gi khrid sogs /
NK125(co)004:907: bde dge'i bla ma rab 'byams pa /
NK125(co)004:908: go 'jo rtsed rong sogs nas lhag pa'i don gnyen can gyi dpon slob mang por /
NK125(co)004:910: thugs rje chen po'i rtsa dbang /
NK125(co)004:912: tshe gur sogs kyi dbang dang /
NK125(co)004:913: dge tshul slong gi sdom pa /
NK125(co)004:914: thugs thig gi khrid la sogs te mchod sbyin rgya
NK125(co)004:915: cher byas pas rang lugs kyi bstan pa shar phyogs
NK125(co)004:916: su dar ba'i lung bstan gyi don bzhin mngon du
NK125(co)004:917: gyur pas bstan pa la bya ba cung zad byas
NK125(co)004:918: so snyam du yid rang bar gyur la /
NK125(co)004:919: phyis rgyal ba 'phags pa lha'i dgongs pa'i gtan mtshams ltar ngag dbang mchog gi sprul pa'i sku dang /
NK125(co)004:920: phyag mdzod rje dbon rin po ches bdag rkyen mdzad
NK125(co)004:921: nas phyogs der rang bstan 'phel rgyas kyi bka' lung
NK125(co)004:922: bzang por byung ba yang rdo'i ri mo bzhin 'gyur
NK125(co)004:923: ba med par gor ma chag go //
NK125(co)004:924: de dus yas mar gyi lam zhong du la mor /
NK125(co)004:925: mar lam chos rje sku rten pa nang 'khor zhabs
NK125(co)004:926: phyi bcas par dkon mchog spyi 'dus kyi dbang dang
NK125(co)004:927: / zhal ngo rnams la tshe dbang /
NK125(co)004:928: yar lam zhal ngo yab yum sras bcas la tshe gur gyi dbang /
NK125(co)004:929: mar lam lha sar bla ma bya bral ba rin po che la tshe dbang /
NK125(co)004:930: sku zhabs grwa gtsang gi grwa pa ngag dbang don grub la dge slong gi sdom pa /
NK125(co)004:931: yar re stag shag gi zhal ngo phun tshan rnams
NK125(co)004:932: la thugs rje chen po'i rtsa dbang dang byad 'grol
NK125(co)004:933: sogs bgyis so // yang bstan pa yun ring du
NK125(co)004:934: gnas par 'dod pa'i lhag bsam gyi rtsom pa than
NK125(co)004:935: sogs bgyis so // thun bgyis pa'ang / sgyu 'phrul
NK125(co)004:936: rtsa rgyud gsang snying la 'grel pa gsang bdag dgongs
NK125(co)004:937: sogs bgyis so // thun bgyis pa'ang / rgyan / spyi don gsang bdag zhal lung /
NK125(co)004:938: dkyil 'khor blos bslangs kyi rnam bzhag gsal sgron rtsa 'grel /
NK125(co)004:939: mdo dbang skor la rnam bshad rgyud lung man ngag gi gnad gsal byed sgron me /
NK125(co)004:940: yan lag gi dkyil 'khor rnams kyi sgrub dkyil dngos grub 'dod 'jo /
NK125(co)004:941: rgyud dang man ngag gi lugs gcig tu dril ba'i dbang chog rdo rje'i them skas /
NK125(co)004:942: sgrub khog rin po che 'od kyi snang ba /
NK125(co)004:944: tsakli'i tho yig gsal ba'i me long /
NK125(co)004:945: rgyud lung la brten pa'i las bzhi'i sbyin sreg ngag 'don 'dod ster dbang rgyal /
NK125(co)004:946: thugs rje chen po bde gshegs kun 'dus kyi sgrub
NK125(co)004:947: thabs rnam bshad de kho na de nyid snang ba'i
NK125(co)004:948: 'od / rdzogs rim spyi'i rnam bshad ri chos yang yod /
NK125(co)004:949: sdom gsum rnam nges kyi 'grel pa legs bshad ngo mtshar dpag bsam snye ma /
NK125(co)004:950: phyag rdor bdud sde phyer 'thag gi las byang rnam nges tshig nyung don rgyas /
NK125(co)004:951: dri med rnam gnyis kyi mchod rten bzhengs chog bklags pas 'grub pa /
NK125(co)004:952: bzang spyod smon lam gyi 'grel pa /
NK125(co)004:953: sdeb sbyor 'grel pa don gsal me long /
NK125(co)004:954: skar rtsis nyin byed snang ba snga brtsams dang /
NK125(co)004:955: phyi brtsams rtsa bar 'phri bsnan gyi rtsam skyor dang /
NK125(co)004:956: dka' 'grel gzhung don snying po legs par 'dren pa'i rta bdun /
NK125(co)004:957: lag len lhan thabs ngo mtshar phreng ba /
NK125(co)004:958: spyi don legs bshad yongs 'du'i snye ma /
NK125(co)004:959: dbyangs 'char mchan 'grel rgyu skar phreng ba /
NK125(co)004:960: gter chen chos kyi rgyal po'i phyi'i rnam thar dad
NK125(co)004:961: pa'i shing rta glegs bam dang po dang gnyis pa
NK125(co)004:962: / nang gi rnam thar yon tan mtha' yas rnam par bkod pa'i rol mo /
NK125(co)004:965: so thar sdom rgyun gyi rnam thar nyung gsal sgron me /
NK125(co)004:966: 'dul ba'i las chog rin chen them skas /
NK125(co)004:967: gzhi gsum gyi cho ga thar gling bgrod pa'i gru chen /
NK125(co)004:968: sku 'bum mthong grol chen po'i dkar chag yid ches kyi nges pa ster byed /
NK125(co)004:969: thugs rje chen po'i blos bslangs dkar chag ngo mtshar yongs 'du'i 'khri shing /
NK125(co)004:970: 'chad nyan byed tshul gyi yi ge mdor bsdus /
NK125(co)004:972: gtor bsngo dang rab gnas stong thun /
NK125(co)004:973: cho ga dang man ngag gi yi ge'i skor la phyi'i chos spyod thar lam rab gsal /
NK125(co)004:974: nang gi chos spyod byang chen spyod pa'i sgron me /
NK125(co)004:975: nyang gter khros nag gi las byang mkha' spyod du bgrod pa'i bde lam /
NK125(co)004:976: bka' brgyad bde 'dus kyi bsnyen yig rin po che'i sgron me /
NK125(co)004:977: phur pa spu gri'i bsnyen yig rin po che'i snye ma /
NK125(co)004:978: rat+na'i drag dmar gyi bsnyen yig nyung gsal sgron me /
NK125(co)004:979: bi ma snying thig gi khrid dmigs brjed byang bdud rtsi'i thig pa /
NK125(co)004:980: gcod kyi khrid yig zab don snying por dril ba /
NK125(co)004:981: thugs rje chen po rgyal po lugs kyi sku gsum snying po'i don khrid kyi khrid yig /
NK125(co)004:982: nyang gter khros nag gi khrid yig zab don gsal ba /
NK125(co)004:983: thugs thig ka dag gi khrid yig dri med snang ba /
NK125(co)004:984: ngo sprod kyi rtsa tho dri med rab gsal /
NK125(co)004:985: dbang gi mtshams sbyor dri med 'od /
NK125(co)004:986: tshe dbang gi mtshams sbyor ngag 'don gsal bder spel ba /
NK125(co)004:987: rdor sems kyi khrid yig rab gsal snang ba /
NK125(co)004:988: khyad par gyi rdzogs rim snang bzhi'i man ngag gi khrid yig mngon sum 'od gsal 'khor lo /
NK125(co)004:989: rmi lam gyi khrid yig nying 'khrul rang grol /
NK125(co)004:990: gcod kyi khrid yig 'khrul rtog dbyings grol /
NK125(co)004:991: thugs rje chen po bde gshegs kun 'dus kyi spros bcas bum dbang gi mtshams sbyor skal ldan kun dga'/
NK125(co)004:992: gnas lung gi cho ga'i ngag 'don /
NK125(co)004:993: bsnyen yig gi zur 'debs bskyur byang /
NK125(co)004:994: rtsa khrid kyi khrid yig sgom don gsal ba'i me long /
NK125(co)004:995: gtum mo'i khrid yig zab gnad gsal sgron /
NK125(co)004:996: 'khrul 'khor gyi rtsa khrid 'chi med bcud ster /
NK125(co)004:997: a ti'i lam rim snying po'i 'grel pa /
NK125(co)004:998: phag mo zab rgya'i 'khrul 'khor gyi rtsa 'grel /
NK125(co)004:999: zhi byed bka' babs gsum gyi dbang chog dang khrid yig cha tshang /
NK125(co)004:1000: gsar rnying spyi 'gro'i dbang bshad rnams so //
NK125(co)004:1001: lag len gyi skor la khrag 'thung khro bo'i rtsa
NK125(co)004:1002: 'chams kyi brjed byang kun bzang rnam par rtsen pa'i
NK125(co)004:1003: rol mo / mchod gar gyi brjed byang mchod sprin rnam par spro ba'i rol mo dang /
NK125(co)004:1004: glu yig rab gsal snang ba /
NK125(co)004:1008: bla ma gsang 'dus kyi dbyangs yig byang bu sogs
NK125(co)004:1009: nyer mkho'i zin bris phran bu mang po yod kyang
NK125(co)004:1012: sgyu 'phrul lam rim gnyis la spyi t+aika re brtsams
NK125(co)004:1013: pa'i dam bca' ri mo yid la bcags rung da
NK125(co)004:1015: drug pa lhag pa'i bsam pas don gnyis 'grub 'gyur la smon lam ji ltar btab tshul ni /
NK125(co)004:1016: de ltar rang nus dang sbyar ba'i 'chad rtsom gyis
NK125(co)004:1017: gzhan phan rnam dkar gyi bya ba cha tsam 'grub
NK125(co)004:1018: pa ltar / slad ma'i char yang tshe mjug 'di
NK125(co)004:1019: dang phyi ma'i skyes rabs kyi phreng bar dus gsum
NK125(co)004:1020: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi spyi gzugs gter chen chos
NK125(co)004:1021: kyi rgyal po rigs bdag tu mi 'bral zhing zab
NK125(co)004:1022: don man ngag gi bdud rtsi ngom pa med par
NK125(co)004:1024: gzhan don phrin las rgya che rgyun mi chad pa dpag bsam gyi shing dang /
NK125(co)004:1026: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che ltar 'bad rtsol med par lhun gyis grub pas /
NK125(co)004:1027: thub bstan spyi dang bye brag snga 'gyur rdo rje
NK125(co)004:1028: theg pa'i bstan pa rin po che 'gro ba'i mchod
NK125(co)004:1029: sdong du mi nub pa'i nyi ma dang /
NK125(co)004:1030: mi 'grib pa'i zla ba ltar 'dzin skyong spel gsum
NK125(co)004:1031: gyi bya ba rlabs po ches srid matha'i bar du
NK125(co)004:1032: dar zhing rgyas par byed nus pa'i skyes bu mthu
NK125(co)004:1034: de kho na bzhin du 'grub par byin gyis rlob tu gsol lo //
NK125(co)004:1035: zhes smon lam btab pa ltar chos thams cad smon
NK125(co)004:1036: lam gyi mtha' bsgyur ba'i phyi gdon mi za bar
NK125(co)004:1037: 'grub pa ste / 'jam dpal gyi zhing gi yon tan bkod pa las /
NK125(co)004:1038: chos rnams thams cad rkyen yin te //
NK125(co)004:1039: 'dun pa'i rtse la rab tu gnas //
NK125(co)004:1040: gang gis smon lam ci btab pa //
NK125(co)004:1041: de ni de bzhin nyid du 'grub //
NK125(co)004:1044: gang dang gang du dam chos 'jig pa der /
NK125(co)004:1045: me tshogs spu gri'i so yang brgal nas ni //
NK125(co)004:1046: phyi mthar thug gi bar du dam chos bzung //
NK125(co)004:1047: zhes pa lta bu'i snying stobs kyis dam chos ma
NK125(co)004:1048: lus pa yongs su 'dzin par bsngosa par gyur na
NK125(co)004:1049: ni / smon lam thams cad kyang rgya mtsho chen
NK125(co)004:1050: por chu klung ji snyed 'jug pa ltar 'du ba
NK125(co)004:1051: ni / bzhed de / bzang po spyod pa'i mdo las /
NK125(co)004:1052: rgyal ba kun gyi dam pa'i chos 'dzin cing //
NK125(co)004:1053: byang chub spyod pa kun tu snang bar byed //
NK125(co)004:1054: bzang po spyod pa rnam par sbyong ba yang //
NK125(co)004:1055: ma 'ongs bskal pa kun tu spyod par shog /
NK125(co)004:1057: ngag tshig bden pa'i gtam gyi 'bab stegs las //
NK125(co)004:1058: rna ba'i dbang por snyan 'jebs bdud rtsi'i klung //
NK125(co)004:1059: chos grogs na tshod mthun dbang blo mtsho la //
NK125(co)004:1060: babs pas yid ches dga' ba'i dpal thob shog 1 /
NK125(co)004:1061: gang 'dir mkhas rnams spyan ras mi g.yo zhing //
NK125(co)004:1062: blun rnams brag cha bzhin las rtog dpyod bral //
NK125(co)004:1063: gzur gnas rgyus yod blo ngor bden gtam ste //
NK125(co)004:1064: phyogs zhen rgyus can rna ba'i bdud rtsir myong /
NK125(co)004:1066: 2 / mkhas rmongs kun gyi snying la thun mong du //
NK125(co)004:1067: babs pa'i gtam gyi sbyor ba sus 'chad nus //
NK125(co)004:1068: de phyir re dogs 'ching ba las grol bas //
NK125(co)004:1069: dam pa'i gsung ngor ma bcos lhug par smras /
NK125(co)004:1071: 3 / dag snang can la khyi sor ring bsrel bzhin //
NK125(co)004:1072: 'di las rnam dkar dge 'bras 'byung srin na //
NK125(co)004:1073: mtha' yas lus can yongs la khyab par bsngo //
NK125(co)004:1074: kun kyang byang chen spyod mchog mtha' phyin shog 4 /
NK125(co)004:1075: ces pa 'di yang mnyam pa med pa'i bka' drin
NK125(co)004:1076: can rje bla ma mchog gi bka' lung spyi bor
NK125(co)004:1077: phebs par ltar / dge slong blo gsal rgya mtshos
NK125(co)004:1078: dar dkar srid du ring ba dang bcas gsung la
NK125(co)004:1079: zhabs mthun gyis bskul ba dang /
NK125(co)004:1080: nye bar gnas pa dge slong kun bloos kyang yang yang gsos btab cing /
NK125(co)004:1081: khyad par rgyal ba 'phags pa lha'i thugs kyi sras
NK125(co)004:1082: ngag dbang mchog gi sprul pa'i sku'i zhal snga nas
NK125(co)004:1083: dngul srang gsum dang byams pa kha btags kyi gnang
NK125(co)004:1084: sbyin dang bcas te gsung gis bskul ba'i ngor mdo
NK125(co)004:1085: khams kyi sa'i thig le chab mdo byams pa gling
NK125(co)004:1086: du dbu btsugs pa las 'phro cung zad lus pa
NK125(co)004:1087: phyis rje bla ma dam pas kyang gsar brtsams mdo
NK125(co)004:1088: dbang rnam bshad kyi dpe rdo rje brag rig 'dzin
NK125(co)004:1089: sprul pa'i sku'i spyan sngar 'bul bar mdzad pa la
NK125(co)004:1090: shin tu dgyes pa'i gzigs pa rnam par dag pas
NK125(co)004:1091: rang nyid kyi rnam thar zhig kyang rtsom par rigs
NK125(co)004:1092: zhes bka' lam du stsal 'dug pa ltar rang lo
NK125(co)004:1093: drug cu pa chu sbrul hor zla drug pa'i tshes
NK125(co)004:1094: bcu gcig lhag pa lha mtshams kyi 'grub sbyor 'dzom
NK125(co)004:1095: pa'i nyin gyi nyi shar phyi cha bdud rtsi thun
NK125(co)004:1097: dge slong rmongs pa d+harma sh+r+ais rang gnas 'chi med
NK125(co)004:1098: 'od snang du grub par sbyar ba'i yi ge pa
NK125(co)004:1099: ni legs gling chos mdzad dge slong 'gyur med mchog
NK125(co)004:1100: grub kyis bgyis pa dge legs 'phel//
